{{version030}}
''This page refers to the monster spell. For the god-given ability, see [[Lugonu#Given Abilities|Lugonu]].''
{{flavour|Unleashes Abyssal energies in the immediate vicinity. This changes the appearance of the affected area and temporarily summons creatures from the Abyss. This cannot be used in the Abyss itself.}}
'''Corrupt''' is a monster-only spell that functions similarly to the ability granted by [[Lugonu]]. It alters the appearance of the surrounding terrain, and may (temporarily) create new features like walls. It also summons 1-3 random creatures found in the [[Abyss]].<ref>{{source ref|0.30.0|abyss.cc|2327}}</ref><ref>{{source ref|0.30.0|abyss.cc|1871}}<br>See {{source ref|0.30.0|mon-pick-data.h|802}} for the full list.</ref> Unlike the player version, it cannot destroy walls, and can be used more than once on a given floor.

{{monsters with spell}}

==History==
*The monster version of Corrupt was added in [[0.28]].

